title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: When calling the IMetaData.getColumnLabel() method before and after data extraction, the returned results are different.
EB: The IMetaData.getColumnLabel() method should consistently return user recognizable strings before and after data extraction.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 
1. Call the IMetaData.getColumnLabel() method before data extraction.
2. Extract the data.
3. Call the IMetaData.getColumnLabel() method again after data extraction. Compare the results.
